{"type": "article", "id": 19259, "title": "内容有趣印刷精美的图册，用作礼物又有何不可？", "description": "我们推荐的是 5 本英文书，它们大多为艺术类、生活类图册。", "date": "2015-12-18T07:20:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 925, "name": "圣诞节"}, {"id": 5504, "name": "礼物"}, {"id": 19383, "name": "书籍"}, {"id": 19676, "name": "精装书"}, {"id": 20593, "name": "画册"}, {"id": 20594, "name": "建筑书"}], "category": 5, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 127, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702151417GU9nVrzhAl7s2pfu.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t礼物真挺难选的，特别是朋友间送礼，要是太贵重呢，收礼人心理压力大，太便宜呢，又显得好轻薄，你还得费尽心思揣摩对方缺点儿什么。我觉得送本精装的摄影/建筑/生活书是最好的啦，它彰显了你的品味，价格也合理。英文书读起来有点费劲，画册则不同，它小众但易读。以下是 5 本新近出版的图册：\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:center;\">Space, Hope and Brutalism</span> \r\n</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151403udV51RtheZYW4SmX.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"582\" title=\"Space, Hope and Brutalism: English Architecture 1945–1975 By Elain Harwood\" alt=\"Space, Hope and Brutalism: English Architecture 1945–1975 By Elain Harwood\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Space, Hope and Brutalism: English Architecture 1945–1975,作者是 Elain Harwood</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151404wnRlI0gCzQZrGFkX.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"582\" title=\"书内插图\" alt=\"书内插图\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>先来看几张书中插图吧</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151404bSdQZ3HCBsl8iw2L.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"582\" title=\"书中插图\" alt=\"书中插图\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>书中的建筑插图</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021514052PcbLmtGEiCFfHJI.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"582\" title=\"插图\" alt=\"插图\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\">插图\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151406pKUrCcyLZa4uGJtk.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"582\" title=\"插图\" alt=\"插图\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t建筑书总是给人冷冰冰的感觉，但这本书稍有不同。从大学到图书馆，从运动场到咖啡厅，它介绍的是 <span>1945 </span>年到 <span>1975 </span>年间建造的英国建筑，同时也是一部英国社会史。这本书是今年新近出版的，有大量的新图片，但书中的建筑却在一个个消失。适合送给将要去英国读书的友人。这本书在美国亚马逊上有售，点击<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Space-Hope-Brutalism-Architecture-1945%C2%961975/dp/0300204469/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1450327251&amp;sr=8-1&amp;keywords=Space%2C+Hope+and+Brutalism\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>尝试购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;background-color:transparent;\"><span style=\"text-align:center;\">Anthony Gormley on Sculpture</span></span> \r\n</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;background-color:transparent;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:left;background-color:transparent;\"></span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151406sUYymdoDTc8r2fbv.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"582\" title=\"Anthony Gormley on Sculpture By Anthony Gormley\" alt=\"Anthony Gormley on Sculpture By Anthony Gormley\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Anthony Gormley on Sculpture ，作者是 Anthony Gormley</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:center;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:center;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151407TIPfK6znSYwRch9H.jpg\" width=\"929\" height=\"944\" title=\"书的内页\" alt=\"书的内页\" data-ratio=\"1.01614639\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>书的内页</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151408c0gHGT5djP3LAUxR.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"582\" title=\"内页\" alt=\"内页\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>真人大小的雕塑</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151409qMEldmgGRZIL1Bk0.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"713\" title=\"内页\" alt=\"内页\" data-ratio=\"0.75052632\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151410ufHrDmFnYEkRUswc.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"774\" title=\"内页\" alt=\"内页\" data-ratio=\"0.81473684\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>陶土人，艺术装置</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这本书就要更感性、更艺术一些。 Antony Gormley 是当代著名的雕塑和装置艺术家，他创作了不少别出新意的建筑作品。比如，他曾做过 31 个真人大小的艺术家雕塑，将它们放在麦迪逊广场上；还曾将成千上万的泥人堆在地板上。他不断地探索人类的形态和物质世界。这本书同样在美国亚马逊上有售，点击<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Antony-Gormley-Sculpture/dp/022631782X/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1450327307&amp;sr=8-1&amp;keywords=Anthony+Gormley+on+Sculpture\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>尝试购买。\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t<span><span style=\"text-align:center;\">1972, Noritaka Minami</span></span> \r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151410EK4pnUjgLF9h8zvA.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"582\" title=\"1972, Noritaka Minami By Julian Rose and Ken Yoshida\" alt=\"1972, Noritaka Minami By Julian Rose and Ken Yoshida\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\">1972, Noritaka Minami 作者是 Julian Rose 和 Ken Yoshida\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151411k1QfbMx9Y0RcC65w.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"760\" title=\"内页\" alt=\"内页\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>内页，胶囊房间的窗户</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151412LYqQD1gC8hwZdvxy.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"760\" title=\"内页\" alt=\"内页\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\">胶囊房间内部\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021514132awbEVqCD0LUXBTs.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"864\" title=\"内页\" alt=\"内页\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span><span style=\"text-align:left;\"></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这本书就更好玩了，它获得了不少建筑出版大奖。<span>Noritaka Minami </span>用手中的相机记录下了建筑师黑川纪章（<span>Kisho Kurokawa</span>）设计的舱体大楼。<span>1972 </span>年，位于东京的舱体大楼竣工，它由 <span>140 </span>个胶囊房间组成，是可移动的。这是“新陈代谢”建筑实验的一部分，而黑川纪章则是<span><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/133435.htm\">新陈代谢派</a></span>的创始人。所谓的新陈代谢运动，是将进化论引入建筑设计，向机器时代宣战、宣告生命时代到来。黑川纪章曾与和<span><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/478213.htm\">矶崎新</a></span>、<span><a href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/view/482627.htm\">安藤忠雄</a></span>并称日本建筑界三杰。这本书在美国亚马逊上有售，点击<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/1972-Nakagin-Capsule-Noritaka-Minami/dp/3868285482/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1450327346&amp;sr=8-1&amp;keywords=1972%2C+Noritaka+Minami\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>尝试购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t<strong><span style=\"text-align:center;\">Please send this book to my mother</span></strong> \r\n</h4>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021514147kiyYjEHo2nUp58b.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"582\" title=\"Please send this book to my mother\" alt=\"Please send this book to my mother\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Please send this book to my mother</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151414TuqMkVaJcO89KjzE.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"720\" title=\"内页\" alt=\"内页\" data-ratio=\"0.75789474\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>内页</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span><span style=\"text-align:left;\"></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t书名很酷！乍看上去像在什么咖啡店随手捡到的一本笔记本。其实这是女艺术家 <span>Sarah Entwistle </span>的艺术传记。它集合了作者来自巴黎、\r\n伦敦、丹吉尔和纽约的艺术作品，还有有趣的人生故事。美国亚马逊上的书很全啊，点击<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Sarah-Entwistle-Please-Send-Mother/dp/3956791533/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1450327377&amp;sr=8-1&amp;keywords=Please+send+this+book+to+my+mother\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>尝试购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<h4>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:center;\">Hartwood</span> \r\n</h4>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151415gTPVvGa9CWyI6rMX.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"582\" title=\"Hartwood: bright, wild flavors from the edge of the Yucatán By Eric Werner and Mya Henry\" alt=\"Hartwood: bright, wild flavors from the edge of the Yucatán By Eric Werner and Mya Henry\" data-ratio=\"0.61263158\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>Hartwood 作者是 Eric Werner 和 Mya Henry</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021514167S9oJuhcanUiRQyW.jpg\" width=\"950\" height=\"796\" title=\"内页\" alt=\"内页\" data-ratio=\"0.83789474\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>内页</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151416pPmZfHhRBFLr36y9.jpg\" width=\"770\" height=\"944\" title=\"内页\" alt=\"内页\" data-ratio=\"1.22597403\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>内页</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t这可是今年最有艺术感的烹饪书了。Eric Werner 和 Mya Henry 是一对勇敢的年轻夫妇，他们放弃了纽约餐厅的厨师工作，在墨西哥的 Tulum 开始了自己的新事业——创办了 Hartwood 餐厅，这是一本食谱书，穿插着精美的照片。点击<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Hartwood-Bright-Wild-Flavors-Yucat%C3%A1n/dp/157965620X/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1450327415&amp;sr=8-1&amp;keywords=Hartwood\" target=\"_blank\">这里</a>可以买到。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.wallpaper.com/gallery/lifestyle/christmas-books-we-round-up-the-top-gift-worthy-titles-of-this-festive-season#139429\" target=\"_blank\">wallpaper</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:center;\"></span> \r\n</div>\n\n"}